=begin

Will automatically listen to anyone iniating a class to you, or will listen to any class that another person joins.  Also, if you are teaching, will smile to all those who join your class.

=end

no_kill_all
no_pause_all
silence_me
main:
listener, teacher = matchfindword "? must LISTEN TO ?", "? begins to listen to ? teach"

if teacher =~ /you/
	pause
	pause
	pause
	pause
	pause
	fput "smile #{listener}"
	goto "main"
else
	fput "listen to #{teacher}"
	goto "main"
end
